====Usage notes====
Some find the use of '''articulate''' condescending, especially to refer to African-American public figures who are skilled at public speaking, and recommend instead {{term|eloquent}}.<ref>[http://www.slate.com/id/2159132/ Obama Messiah Watch, Part 2: A Harvard Law wunderkind masters laws that govern the universe], by Timothy Noah</ref>

