* {{audio|en-us-articulate-adj.ogg|Audio (US)|lang=en}}

====Adjective====
{{en-adj}}

# [[clear]], [[effective]]
# especially, [[speak]]ing in a clear or effective manner
#: {{ux|en|She’s a bright, '''articulate''' young woman.}}
# able to [[bend]] or [[hinge]] at certain points or [[interval]]s
#: {{ux|en|The robot arm was '''articulate''' in two directions.}}
#: {{ux|en|'''articulate''' animals or plants}}
# Expressed in articles or in separate items or particulars.
#: {{rfquotek|Francis Bacon}}
# {{lb|en|obsolete|of sound}} Related to [[human]] speech, as distinct from the [[vocalisation]] of [[animal]]s.
